data.description: Modern Turnkey 3BD, 2BTH, 2 CAR GARAGE.NEW KITCHEN, NEW CABINETS, NEW APPLIANCES in sought after gated community of Estancia, whether you are looking for a tranquil retreat or a vibrant community, this home has everything you need to live your best life. Modern kitchen, new cabinetry, custom pantry, w/ large center island for cooking, with quartz countertops, and new laminated floors throughout all the living areas. Eat in kitchen with formal dining area. NEW ROOF! Renovated bathrooms, freshly painted with neutral colors.  Low HOA with community pool, new gym, basketball court and playground. Centrally located in West Pembroke Pines Close to US-27 & I-75. This area offers A plus schools.
